snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Lawyer DESTROYS Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's Lawyer DESTROYS Amber Heard
______________________________________________
For more videos subscribe : https://bit.ly/2zoPgqj
______________________________________________
Many of us are quite aware with the Depp Heard situation and well while things have heated down for quite a bit both are taking quite a few blows at each other.

If you've seen our previous videos you know how the trial has changed things for Johnny Depp for the
worse while many have supported him in the past. A few others have spoken against him however apparently something has come up in the court and the kind of change it invites in the trial is quite shocking.
